                  <collation>
                     <p>The quires, 16 in number, are signed with both letters and arithmetical figures (e. g. <locus from="20a" to="20a">fol. 20 a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܓ</foreign>, <locus from="70a" to="70a">fol. 70 a</locus>,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚ</foreign>).</p><!-- Arabic numbers on top of these letters -->
                  </collation>
                  <condition>
