                         <p>Some leaves are much stained and torn, especially foll.<locus from="10" to="10">10</locus>, and <locus from="154" to="157">154 —157</locus>.</p>
                      </item>
                       <item>
                          <p>One leaf is wanting at the beginning, and another after <locus from="149" to="149">fol. 149</locus>.</p>
                       </item>
                    </list>
                  </condition>
